{"ja478:0.1":"Jataka ","ja478:0.2":"Terasakanipata ","ja478:0.3":"Ambavagga ","ja478:0.4":"5. Dutajataka ","ja478:1.1":"“Dute te brahme pahesim, ","ja478:1.2":"Gangatirasmi jhayato; ","ja478:1.3":"Tesam puttho na byakasi, ","ja478:1.4":"Dukkham guyhamatam nu te”. ","ja478:2.1":"“Sace te dukkhamuppajje, ","ja478:2.2":"kasinam ratthavaddhana; ","ja478:2.3":"Ma kho nam tassa akkhahi, ","ja478:2.4":"yo tam dukkha na mocaye. ","ja478:3.1":"Yo tassa dukkhajatassa, ","ja478:3.2":"ekangamapi bhagaso; ","ja478:3.3":"Vippamoceyya dhammena, ","ja478:3.4":"kamam tassa pavedaya. ","ja478:4.1":"Suvijanam singalanam, ","ja478:4.2":"sakunananca vassitam; ","ja478:4.3":"Manussavassitam raja, ","ja478:4.4":"dubbijanataram tato. ","ja478:5.1":"Api ce mannati poso, ","ja478:5.2":"nati mitto sakhati va; ","ja478:5.3":"Yo pubbe sumano hutva, ","ja478:5.4":"paccha sampajjate diso. ","ja478:6.1":"Yo attano dukkhamananuputtho, ","ja478:6.2":"Pavedaye jantu akalarupe; ","ja478:6.3":"Anandino tassa bhavantimitta, ","ja478:6.4":"Hitesino tassa dukhi bhavanti. ","ja478:7.1":"Kalanca natvana tathavidhassa, ","ja478:7.2":"Medhavinam ekamanam viditva; ","ja478:7.3":"Akkheyya tibbani parassa dhiro, ","ja478:7.4":"Sanham giram atthavatim pamunce. ","ja478:8.1":"Sace ca janna avisayhamattano, ","ja478:8.2":"Na te hi mayham sukhagamaya; ","ja478:8.3":"Ekova tibbani saheyya dhiro, ","ja478:8.4":"Saccam hirottappamapekkhamano. ","ja478:9.1":"Aham ratthe vicaranto, ","ja478:9.2":"nigame rajadhaniyo; ","ja478:9.3":"Bhikkhamano maharaja, ","ja478:9.4":"acariyassa dhanatthiko. ","ja478:10.1":"Gahapati rajapurise, ","ja478:10.2":"mahasale ca brahmane; ","ja478:10.3":"Alattham satta nikkhani, ","ja478:10.4":"suvannassa janadhipa; ","ja478:10.5":"Te me nattha maharaja, ","ja478:10.6":"tasma socamaham bhusam. ","ja478:11.1":"Purisa te maharaja, ","ja478:11.2":"manasanuvicintita; ","ja478:11.3":"Nalam dukkha pamocetum, ","ja478:11.4":"tasma tesam na byaharim. ","ja478:12.1":"Tvanca kho me maharaja, ","ja478:12.2":"manasanuvicintito; ","ja478:12.3":"Alam dukkha pamocetum, ","ja478:12.4":"tasma tuyham pavedayim”. ","ja478:13.1":"“Tassadasi pasannatto, ","ja478:13.2":"kasinam ratthavaddhano; ","ja478:13.3":"Jatarupamaye nikkhe, ","ja478:13.4":"suvannassa catuddasa”ti. ","ja478:14.1":"Dutajatakam pancamam. "}